high_descs: Turn right and look at the left side of the table
Grab the knife off of the table
Turn around and go to the fridge
Slice the lettuce in the fridge
Back up from the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Move forward towards the fridge
Grab a slice of lettuce out of the fridge
Turn around and go to the sink
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the left of the table
Put the lettuce on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting clean sliced lettuce on a table

high_descs: Turn right to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Cut the lettuce in the fridge into slices.
Look up to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Look up to face the fridge.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from in the fridge.
Turn left and step forward to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and remove it.
Turn around and walk forward and turn right to face the table.
Place the lettuce slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: To wash a slice of lettuce and place it on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Face the table to your right.
Take the knife from the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the fridge in front of you.
Slice the lettuce inside of the fridge in front of you and close it.
Turn left and face the fridge to your right.
Place the knife in the fridge and close it.
Turn right and face the fridge on your left.
Take a lettuce slice from the fridge in front of you and close it.
Turn left and face the counter by the microwave in front of you.
Wash the lettuce in the sink in front of you and take it out.
Turn around and face the table to your right.
Place the lettuce slice on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean lettuce slice on the table.
